  recommended_activities_en = E'• Fasting\n• Night vigil with chanting Vishnu''s names\n• Offering fruits: mangoes, coconuts, pomegranates, amla\n• Reading 108 Names of Sri Narasimha\n• Chanting Vishnu mantras',

